<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><b>phpMyAdmin Installation on FreeBSD</b></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: underline;"><font style="font-size: 24px;">phpMyAdmin (MySQL or MariaDB )</font></span></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">=&gt; </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">cd</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;"> /usr/ports/databases/phpmyadmin/</span></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">=&gt; sudo </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">make install clean</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">This will install the </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">phpMyAdmin</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;"> into </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">/usr/local/<a href="http://www/phpMyAdmin">www/phpMyAdmin</a></span></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">Edit </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">config.inc.php</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;"> to suit your needs.</span></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">Edit the Apache main config file </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #ff40ff;"> /usr/local/etc/apache24/</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #941751;">httpd.conf</span></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">and add the lines inside the</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #0433ff;"> &lt;</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">IfModule</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2f92;">alias_module</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #0433ff;">&gt;</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #0433ff;"></span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;"> directory:</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #5e5e5e;"># phpMyAdmin Access</span></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">    </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2f92;">Alias</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #008f00;">/phpmyadmin</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #ff40ff;">/usr/local/<a href="http://www/phpMyAdmin">www/phpMyAdmin</a></span></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">        </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">&lt;Directory</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #ff40ff;">/usr/local/<a href="http://www/phpMyAdmin">www/phpMyAdmin</a></span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">&gt;</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;"></span></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">           </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #0096ff; font-weight: bold;">Options</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;"> None</span></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">           </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #0096ff; font-weight: bold;">AllowOverride</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;"> Limit</span></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">           </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #0096ff; font-weight: bold;">Require</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2600;"> local</span></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">          </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"> </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #0096ff; font-weight: bold;">Require</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;"> ip</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;"> </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2600;">192.168.100. </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #5e5e5e;">allow from these subfolders to use the</span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2600;"> </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">phpMyAdmin </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; color: #ff2600;"> </span></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">        </span><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica; font-weight: bold;">&lt;/Directory&gt;</span></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font: 17.0px Helvetica;">Note: You might need: =&gt; sudo chmod 644 /usr/local/<a href="http://www/phpMyAdmin/config.inc.php">www/phpMyAdmin/config.inc.php</a></span></div></en-note>